---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Inschrijvingen" description="Inschrijven bij Sint-Victor Alsemberg voor schooljaar 2026-2027.">

  <section class="bg-[#07153b] text-white py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-yellow-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Schooljaar 2026-2027</div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-4">Inschrijvingen</h1>
      <p class="text-blue-200 text-lg max-w-2xl">Welkom bij Sint-Victor! Hier vind je alle info over inschrijven voor het nieuwe schooljaar.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">

      <!-- 1ste jaar -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
          <div class="w-1 h-8 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full"></div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#07153b]">1ste jaar 2026-2027</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-8 pl-4">Inschrijvingen voor het eerste jaar verlopen via het centraal aanmeldingssysteem <strong class="text-gray-700">aanmelden.school</strong>, in samenwerking met andere regionale scholen.</p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8">

          <!-- Stap 1 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="bg-[#07153b] text-yellow-400 font-extrabold rounded-full w-9 h-9 flex items-center justify-center text-sm shrink-0">1</div>
              <h3 class="font-extrabold text-[#07153b]">Informeer je</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">Lees de brochure en bezoek onze opendeurdag om het aanbod te ontdekken.</p>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <a href="/Brochure Aanmelden 2627.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
                class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-bold text-[#07153b] bg-yellow-50 hover:bg-yellow-100 transition px-3 py-2 rounded-lg">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3m2 8H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
                </svg>
                Brochure aanmelden 2026-2027
              </a>
              <a href="https://www.info-avonden.be" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
                class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-bold text-[#07153b] bg-gray-50 hover:bg-blue-50 transition px-3 py-2 rounded-lg">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                Op stap naar het secundair onderwijs
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Stap 2 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="bg-[#07153b] text-yellow-400 font-extrabold rounded-full w-9 h-9 flex items-center justify-center text-sm shrink-0">2</div>
              <h3 class="font-extrabold text-[#07153b]">Meld je aan</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">Aanmelden gebeurt via het centrale platform <strong>aanmelden.school</strong>. Daar geef je je schoolkeuzes in volgorde van voorkeur in.</p>
            <a href="https://www.aanmelden.school" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
              class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-bold text-white bg-[#07153b] hover:bg-blue-900 transition px-3 py-2 rounded-lg">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14" />
              </svg>
              Naar aanmelden.school
            </a>
          </div>

          <!-- Stap 3 -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="bg-[#07153b] text-yellow-400 font-extrabold rounded-full w-9 h-9 flex items-center justify-center text-sm shrink-0">3</div>
              <h3 class="font-extrabold text-[#07153b]">Schrijf je in</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">Na de aanmeldingsperiode ontvang je bericht. Daarna kom je je kind effectief inschrijven op school. Breng mee:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex gap-2 items-start">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#07153b] shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                Rapport 6de leerjaar
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-2 items-start">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#07153b] shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                CLB-advies (indien van toepassing)
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-2 items-start">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#07153b] shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                Identiteitsdocument kind
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 rounded-2xl p-5 flex gap-4 items-start">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#07153b] shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            Sint-Victor Alsemberg werkt samen met andere regionale scholen via het gecentraliseerde aanmeldingssysteem. Meer info over de aanmeldingsprocedure en -periodes vind je op <a href="https://www.aanmelden.school" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-[#07153b] font-bold hover:underline">aanmelden.school</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Zij-instromers -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
          <div class="w-1 h-8 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full"></div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-[#07153b]">Zij-instromers (2de&ndash;6de jaar)</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-8 pl-4">Wil je overstappen van een andere school naar Sint-Victor? Neem dan eerst contact op met ons secretariaat om de mogelijkheden te bespreken.</p>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-extrabold text-[#07153b] mb-3">Hoe verloopt dit?</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                Neem telefonisch of per mail contact op met het secretariaat
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                We bespreken samen of er een geschikte richting beschikbaar is
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                Breng het attest van het vorige schooljaar mee bij de inschrijving
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3 items-start">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                Een persoonlijk gesprek is steeds mogelijk
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 shrink-0">
            <a href="tel:+3223801589" class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#07153b] text-white font-bold px-5 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-blue-900 transition text-sm">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
              </svg>
              02 380 15 89
            </a>
            <a href="mailto:info@sintvictor.be" class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-gray-50 text-[#07153b] font-bold px-5 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-blue-50 transition text-sm border border-gray-200">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
              </svg>
              info@sintvictor.be
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Onderste 3 blokjes -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {[
          {
            titel: "Infobrochure",
            tekst: "Download onze brochure voor schooljaar 2026-2027 met alle praktische info over aanmelden.",
            link: "/Brochure Aanmelden 2627.pdf",
            linkTekst: "Download PDF",
            extern: true,
          },
          {
            titel: "Opendeurdag",
            tekst: "Bezoek onze school op zaterdag 16 mei 2026 van 9u tot 12u. Gratis en zonder afspraak.",
            link: "/contact",
            linkTekst: "Meer info",
            extern: false,
          },
          {
            titel: "Vragen?",
            tekst: "Neem contact op met ons secretariaat via info@sintvictor.be of bel ons op 02 380 15 89.",
            link: "/contact",
            linkTekst: "Contacteer ons",
            extern: false,
          },
        ].map(i => (
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-6 text-center hover:bg-blue-50 transition border border-transparent hover:border-[#07153b]/20">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#07153b]/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#07153b]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-[#07153b] mb-2">{i.titel}</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed">{i.tekst}</p>
            <a href={i.link} target={i.extern ? "_blank" : undefined} rel={i.extern ? "noopener" : undefined}
              class="text-[#07153b] text-sm font-bold hover:underline">{i.linkTekst} &rarr;</a>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
